1
00:01:46,083 --> 00:01:48,041
[shimmering]

2
00:01:48,125 --> 00:01:50,625
[explosions]

3
00:01:54,666 --> 00:01:58,625
How disappointing. I thought
it would be more of a challenge.

4
00:01:58,708 --> 00:01:59,791
Man.

5
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:10,666
[YUUKI] Tomb guardians
and tomb raiders.

6
00:02:10,750 --> 00:02:13,208
These two opposing forces
have endlessly fought

7
00:02:13,291 --> 00:02:15,625
over the Goddess’s tomb
for a millennium,

8
00:02:15,708 --> 00:02:18,250
one side invading,
the other protecting.

9
00:02:19,250 --> 00:02:20,708
But in the distant past,

10
00:02:20,791 --> 00:02:23,000
both sides had
the same special powers.

11
00:02:24,041 --> 00:02:25,458
How did we ever come to this?

12
00:02:25,541 --> 00:02:27,000
This is your mess, Twin!

13
00:02:27,083 --> 00:02:28,958
Hurry and fix it, Star!

14
00:02:29,041 --> 00:02:30,791
[EEYUU]
Charge complete.

15
00:02:30,875 --> 00:02:32,083
[chuckles]

16
00:02:32,166 --> 00:02:33,625
Fire!

17
00:02:33,708 --> 00:02:36,083
-[explosions]
-[rumbling]

18
00:02:48,375 --> 00:02:50,666
[SHIN]
The left leg's gone, Twin!

19
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:52,541
[WEI]
Game over, Star!

20
00:02:52,625 --> 00:02:54,458
Young Master, we should retreat!

21
00:02:54,541 --> 00:02:55,916
[beeping]

22
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:59,000
Come on. Please!

23
00:02:59,083 --> 00:03:00,791
Perfect!

24
00:03:00,875 --> 00:03:03,958
We’ll fight fire with fire!

25
00:03:04,041 --> 00:03:05,916
Okay. I’m with you!

26
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,041
[scoffs]

27
00:03:10,916 --> 00:03:14,000
[YUUKI] The tomb raiders'
only ambition is to destroy

28
00:03:14,083 --> 00:03:16,500
and take the power
of the gods for themselves.

29
00:03:19,625 --> 00:03:22,166
[FARIN] What is that?
It’s gigantic!

30
00:03:23,208 --> 00:03:26,041
[YUUKI] So we, the Guardians,
safeguard the power

31
00:03:26,125 --> 00:03:29,833
that lies within these
sacred sites, and the world.

32
00:03:29,916 --> 00:03:31,833
This is our eternal duty.

33
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:39,041
[SUIGIN]
Found ‘em!

34
00:03:39,125 --> 00:03:42,541
No need to rush.
Aim carefully.

35
00:03:42,625 --> 00:03:45,208
You got it. I won’t fail you.

36
00:03:45,291 --> 00:03:47,083
But over the ages,

37
00:03:47,166 --> 00:03:50,958
the number of tomb
guardians continued to decline.

38
00:03:51,041 --> 00:03:52,791
And now...

39
00:03:55,583 --> 00:03:56,875
[shots firing]

40
00:04:03,541 --> 00:04:06,166
I gotta recharge again?
I just shot the thing.

41
00:04:06,250 --> 00:04:08,208
Don’t be embarrassed,
it happens.

42
00:04:08,291 --> 00:04:11,208
I could have swore I had it.

43
00:04:11,291 --> 00:04:13,125
[screaming]

44
00:04:15,250 --> 00:04:17,166
[energy bursting]

45
00:04:19,333 --> 00:04:21,125
[exploding]

46
00:04:21,208 --> 00:04:22,666
[yelling]

47
00:04:29,375 --> 00:04:32,333
[PHOEBE] I wouldn’t expect any
less from a guardian’s cannon.

48
00:04:32,416 --> 00:04:34,500
I actually felt that one.

49
00:04:34,583 --> 00:04:35,916
[shattering]

50
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,916
They sure know how
to keep a girl on her toes.

51
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,333
[EEYUU shuddering]

52
00:04:39,416 --> 00:04:42,500
What? Was that too much for you?
Man up.

53
00:04:42,583 --> 00:04:45,458
Uh, no. It wasn’t too much.
I’m just pissed off!

54
00:04:45,541 --> 00:04:49,208
Damn it! Now that does it!
Let’s see how they like it

55
00:04:49,291 --> 00:04:50,583
when I bust out
my ultimate mode.

56
00:04:50,666 --> 00:04:52,875
Then they’ll be sorry!
They'll see!

57
00:04:52,958 --> 00:04:56,000
Yeah. If they want
to play dirty, so be it.

58
00:04:56,083 --> 00:04:58,458
I have more than one card
up my sleeve.

59
00:05:00,458 --> 00:05:01,875
[chuckles]

60
00:05:03,916 --> 00:05:05,333
[shuddering breaths]

61
00:05:09,791 --> 00:05:11,375
Shostia?

62
00:05:11,458 --> 00:05:15,916
The club.
I have to shoot the club.

63
00:05:16,875 --> 00:05:18,583
Here goes!

64
00:05:26,583 --> 00:05:29,500
[evil laughter]

65
00:05:29,583 --> 00:05:32,375
That’s right!
Shoot ‘em all!

66
00:05:39,208 --> 00:05:41,125
[WEI]
We're almost out of power, Star!

67
00:05:41,208 --> 00:05:43,250
[SHIN] And there’s only one
round left in the cannon, Twin!

68
00:05:43,333 --> 00:05:46,666
[WEI] What do you think
you’re doing, Star?

69
00:05:46,750 --> 00:05:48,500
What’s going on, Twin?

70
00:05:48,583 --> 00:05:50,208
You can flirt later, Star!

71
00:05:50,291 --> 00:05:52,583
Help me! I don’t know
what’s wrong with her!

72
00:05:52,666 --> 00:05:54,000
Any clue?

73
00:05:54,083 --> 00:05:57,291
[YUUKI] Oh, my.
Looks like hypnosis. Not good.

74
00:05:57,375 --> 00:05:59,750
[FARIN yelling]

75
00:06:03,125 --> 00:06:04,666
Quick, while it’s down!

76
00:06:07,833 --> 00:06:10,541
[SHIN] The armor’s been
destroyed, Twin!

77
00:06:10,625 --> 00:06:13,958
[WEI] And their familiars are
crawling inside the Giant, Star!

78
00:06:14,041 --> 00:06:16,291
[SUIGIN yelling}

79
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:21,291
Gramps!
Crap, are you okay?

80
00:06:22,666 --> 00:06:24,666
[PHOEBE]
One last push should do it.

81
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:26,958
Hey. Farin, sweetie?

82
00:06:27,041 --> 00:06:29,208
Eeyuu’s about to release
some pent up anger,

83
00:06:29,291 --> 00:06:31,791
so you might want to find
cover and stay there.

84
00:06:31,875 --> 00:06:33,708
Buckle up, fool.

85
00:06:36,333 --> 00:06:37,916
Please don’t come in, Twin!

86
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:40,583
This might be
the end of us, Star.

87
00:06:40,666 --> 00:06:43,708
[SHOSTIA]
Must shoot. The club.

88
00:06:43,791 --> 00:06:45,916
Grandpa. What’s wrong?

89
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:48,333
Come on, talk to me, Gramps!

90
00:06:48,416 --> 00:06:53,083
It's fine. I knew my saved data
would deteriorate eventually.

91
00:06:53,166 --> 00:06:55,541
There’s no need to be sad.

92
00:06:56,666 --> 00:06:59,583
Suigin, listen.

93
00:06:59,666 --> 00:07:05,083
You must protect Bango’s tomb.
If you succeed in this duty,

94
00:07:05,166 --> 00:07:07,375
you will save Rei, as well.

95
00:07:10,166 --> 00:07:12,208
You’re the last guardian.

96
00:07:12,291 --> 00:07:17,041
I know you can do this.
Believe in yourself.

97
00:07:17,125 --> 00:07:18,500
[shimmering]

98
00:07:21,125 --> 00:07:24,375
Go make me proud, Suigin.

99
00:07:27,250 --> 00:07:29,625
[laughing]

100
00:07:29,708 --> 00:07:31,458
I love you!

101
00:07:32,833 --> 00:07:35,166
I will, Gramps. I swear it!

102
00:07:40,791 --> 00:07:42,000
[energy surging]

103
00:07:42,083 --> 00:07:44,125
Pull back. We’re done here!

104
00:07:51,708 --> 00:07:53,875
What is that?

105
00:07:53,958 --> 00:07:56,500
[PHOEBE] Wha--?
Another player’s out there?

106
00:07:56,583 --> 00:07:59,166
No, you must be seeing things.

107
00:07:59,250 --> 00:08:00,666
[EEYUU]
I’m not sure.

108
00:08:01,958 --> 00:08:03,583
♪

109
00:08:05,500 --> 00:08:08,166
Shoot it. Shoot the club.

110
00:08:08,250 --> 00:08:11,458
I have to, no matter what.

111
00:08:11,541 --> 00:08:13,041
[dinging]

112
00:08:13,125 --> 00:08:14,625
-Here goes!
-Here goes!

113
00:08:20,958 --> 00:08:24,041
[FARIN] Crap! I don’t get it.
How is it so fast?

114
00:08:26,416 --> 00:08:28,333
Why is that there?

115
00:08:38,416 --> 00:08:40,208
No. It can’t be!

116
00:08:40,291 --> 00:08:41,750
[exploding]

117
00:08:45,250 --> 00:08:46,666
No, Phoebe!

118
00:08:52,458 --> 00:08:54,625
Dammit! How did this happen?

119
00:08:57,500 --> 00:08:59,208
So you’re behind this?

120
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:05,791
Wait, are you a guardian?

121
00:09:05,875 --> 00:09:07,666
That's impossible!

122
00:09:07,750 --> 00:09:09,125
They all vanished.

123
00:09:09,208 --> 00:09:11,916
They’ve been gone
for a long time now!

124
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,666
There’s one left.

125
00:09:13,750 --> 00:09:14,750
And that’s me.

126
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:18,375
You attacked the wrong tomb.

127
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:20,791
[whimpering]

128
00:09:25,041 --> 00:09:26,458
Damn it!

129
00:09:28,791 --> 00:09:31,416
Disappear!

130
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:32,583
[energy surging]

131
00:09:36,791 --> 00:09:38,500
What the...?

132
00:09:41,708 --> 00:09:43,916
[YUUKI]
I’m counting on you, Suigin.

133
00:09:53,250 --> 00:09:55,166
[SUIGIN]
Did I pass the test?

134
00:09:55,250 --> 00:09:58,375
[SHOSTIA] Yes. Your heroic
victory over the tomb raiders

135
00:09:58,458 --> 00:09:59,708
was proof enough.

136
00:09:59,791 --> 00:10:02,708
You are more than
worthy of the mantle.

137
00:10:02,791 --> 00:10:05,541
Congratulations, Young Master.

138
00:10:05,625 --> 00:10:07,750
Thanks, Shostia.

139
00:10:07,833 --> 00:10:11,125
But, honestly,
I just barely pulled it off

140
00:10:11,208 --> 00:10:13,000
because the three
of you helped me.

141
00:10:13,083 --> 00:10:14,000
[snoring]

142
00:10:17,208 --> 00:10:18,416
No, Young Master.

143
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:21,375
You were already
a splendid tomb guardian.

144
00:10:21,458 --> 00:10:23,833
Thank you.
For everything you’ve done.

145
00:10:25,333 --> 00:10:27,750
I wish I could stay
by your side.

146
00:10:33,500 --> 00:10:35,250
Wha--? Where did...?

147
00:10:36,833 --> 00:10:39,041
This stage and I have
fulfilled our purposes,

148
00:10:39,125 --> 00:10:41,291
and now we both
must come to end.

149
00:10:46,583 --> 00:10:48,500
I know that you’ll save her.

150
00:10:50,458 --> 00:10:53,583
This is goodbye,
Young Master.

151
00:10:56,875 --> 00:10:59,083
Good luck in the battle
to come.

152
00:11:03,333 --> 00:11:05,083
Shostia.

153
00:11:07,041 --> 00:11:10,000
[COLLECTOR (HUMAN) laughing]

154
00:11:10,083 --> 00:11:12,083
A boy’s my competition?

155
00:11:12,166 --> 00:11:14,708
This’ll be even easier
than I thought.

156
00:11:14,791 --> 00:11:16,833
Who are you?

157
00:11:16,916 --> 00:11:20,375
Old man Riku picked a wittle
baby to be the last guardian?

158
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:23,583
So sad it’s almost funny.

159
00:11:23,666 --> 00:11:26,416
Listen up, boy,
and remember well.

160
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:28,250
You’re not the last guardian.

161
00:11:29,416 --> 00:11:32,166
That title belongs to me!

162
00:11:32,250 --> 00:11:33,166
[gunshot]

163
00:11:33,250 --> 00:11:34,250
[gasping, grunting]

164
00:11:37,583 --> 00:11:40,250
[evil laughter]

165
00:13:15,583 --> 00:13:17,666
The Silver Guardian!

